{
  "stem": "23090.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I came out and I met my wife, who is an American woman from Cleveland, a lady.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- we raised three greats kids, and with that, came two wonderful grandkids.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if I look back, if anything good came of everything, this is what came good, is the family and we can continue on [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] with the-- with the family tree, so to speak, with life.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] What else can I say?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What is the family tree now?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The family tree is two sons and a daughter, a wonderful wife, a wonderful person.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Two grandkids that I don't know what I would do without them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I try to tell my kids, I don't like to put a message of pity.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't like to be-- I don't like, and I wish survivors would be more aggressive rather than subdued.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think that-- that-- that my message is-- to anybody, not just young people-- is that this thing can happen any time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It happened very quickly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's going on in the world right now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So nothing really-- nobody paid too much attention.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you have to be alert.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I always tell my kids, very simply, that if something like that, if I had any inclination that something like that would happen again to me, if I sensed it in any way, they would have to carry me out.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I would use every weapon, every conceivable instrument, strength, available.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I would recruit as many as I could as to-- for this thing not to happen to the future generations.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in some way, I believe that [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there might have been a different way other than just going as sheep to the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
